Forwarded from: Ministry of Emergency Situations of Russia
Firefighters from the Russian Ministry of Emergency Situations extinguish a fire in Rostov. A two-story warehouse is on fire in the Leventsovsky microdistrict. The fire engulfed the roof and spread to the roof of the adjacent room. The area is 800 square meters. 50 specialists and 16 units of equipment work on site.@mchs_rostov
